"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?21/42/22180?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Evaluation of the infertile couple (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?1/44/1730?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Gonorrhea (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?24/14/24802?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Chlamydia (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?3/53/3926?source=see_link\">",
